=== 質疑警方無跟指引取《港區國安法》被捕人DNA樣本 ===
協助被捕者的義務律師彭皓昕及義務律師游月華向媒體表示，因藏有宣傳標語，傳單和貼紙而被捕的10人中，其中有6位已被警察採集了頭髮和唾液DNA樣本，質疑無故檢取被告 DNA 可能違反《個人資料（私隱）條例》<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hong Kong police take DNA samples from arrested protesters; lawyer shocked|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3091835/national-security-law-police-take-dna-samples-arrested|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2020-07-04|work=South China Morning Post|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705034806/https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3091835/national-security-law-police-take-dna-samples-arrested|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方引述《警察條例》59C（2a​​）條<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap232!zh-Hant-HK?INDEX_CS=N&xpid=ID_1438402865498_001 |title=《警察條例》 |accessdate=2020-07-05 |archive-date=2020-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828162125/https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/checkconfig/checkClientConfig.jsp?applicationId=RA001 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，稱他們有權收集這10名被捕者的非體內樣本。但根據專門從事刑事案件的香港律師駱應淦指出，  59C (2a)條 一定要與59C (2b) 同時符合才可授權採取樣本。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hong Kong e-Legislation|url=https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/checkconfig/checkClientConfig.jsp?applicationId=RA001|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=www.elegislation.gov.hk|archive-date=2020-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705023144/https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/checkconfig/checkClientConfig.jsp?applicationId=RA001|dead-url=no}}</ref> 因59C (2b)不適用，而59C (3a)又有 規定作出的授權「必須以書面形式作出」，所以有感 香港警察可能越權<ref>{{Cite web|title=警方取國安法被捕人DNA樣本　倘定罪可永久存檔|url=https://www.hkcnews.com/article/31594/國安法-香港警隊-31610/警方取國安法被捕人dna樣本-倘定罪可永久存檔|accessdate=2020-07-29|work=眾新聞|language=zh|archive-date=2020-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705101049/https://www.hkcnews.com/article/31594/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A-31610/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%96%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E4%BA%BAdna%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC-%E5%80%98%E5%AE%9A%E7%BD%AA%E5%8F%AF%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E5%AD%98%E6%AA%94|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他推測提取DNA的主要目的是恐嚇被捕者。另外，當義務律師彭皓昕質疑做法時，報道指有警員說：「你鍾意就JR（司法覆核）喇！」<ref>{{Cite web|title=國安法被捕者扣留期間取 DNA 樣本 律師質疑時警員回應：如有不滿可司法覆核 {{!}} 立場報道 {{!}} 立場新聞|url=https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%80%85%E6%89%A3%E7%95%99%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E5%8F%96-dna-%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%99%82%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-%E5%A6%82%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8/|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=立場新聞 Stand News|language=zh|archive-date=2020-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705034915/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%80%85%E6%89%A3%E7%95%99%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E5%8F%96-dna-%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%99%82%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-%E5%A6%82%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

