=== 國際回應：美國總統簽署《香港自治法》 並取消香港特殊待遇 ===
美國總統[[唐納·川普|特朗普]]於今天簽署了分別獲得參眾兩了院一致通過的《香港自治法》（HR 7440)<ref>{{Cite web|title=S.3798 - 116th Congress (2019-2020): Hong Kong Autonomy Act|url=https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/3798|accessdate=2020-07-15|date=2020-06-29|last=Toomey|first=Pat|work=www.congress.gov|archive-date=2020-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629022819/https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/3798|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此法案授予國務卿90天的期限內對「外國人未能履行《[[中英聯合聲明|中英聯合聲明]]》或《[[中華人民共和國香港特別行政區基本法|香港基本法]]》」及其銀行實施財產及簽証制裁<ref>{{Cite web|title=President Trump Announces Signing of Hong Kong Autonomy Act {{!}} C-SPAN.org|url=https://www.c-span.org/video/?c4892675/president-trump-announces-signing-hong-kong-autonomy-act|accessdate=2020-07-15|work=www.c-span.org|language=en-us|archive-date=2020-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717035717/https://www.c-span.org/video/?c4892675%2Fpresident-trump-announces-signing-hong-kong-autonomy-act|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另一方面，總統特朗普亦簽署了一項行政命令，終止了香港的優惠待遇，以示反對北京在香港頒布國家安全法<ref>{{Cite web|title=特朗普簽《香港自治法》兼取消特殊特遇 指很多人離開香港失競爭優勢 {{!}} 立場報道 {{!}} 立場新聞|url=https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%B0%BD-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB%E6%B3%95-%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E7%89%B9%E9%81%87-%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%B1%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2/|accessdate=2020-07-15|work=立場新聞 Stand News|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715115254/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%B0%BD-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB%E6%B3%95-%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E7%89%B9%E9%81%87-%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%B1%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。特朗普在新聞發佈會上說，現在美國將對香港與中國大陸一視同仁。香港人民的自由在中國頒布國安法時被剝奪了。因此，「將在自由市場失去競爭力，相信不少人會離開香港」<ref>{{Cite web|title=香港自治法｜特朗普簽署《香港自治法案》　終止港特殊待遇 (07:38)|url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200715/s00001/1594769990902/%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae%e7%b0%bd%e7%bd%b2%e3%80%8a%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e8%87%aa%e6%b2%bb%e6%b3%95%e6%a1%88%e3%80%8b-%e7%b5%82%e6%ad%a2%e6%b8%af%e7%89%b9%e6%ae%8a%e5%be%85%e9%81%87|accessdate=2020-07-29|work=明報|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828162157/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200715/s00001/1594769990902/%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e8%87%aa%e6%b2%bb%e6%b3%95-%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae%e7%b0%bd%e7%bd%b2%e3%80%8a%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e8%87%aa%e6%b2%bb%e6%b3%95%e6%a1%88%e3%80%8b-%e7%b5%82%e6%ad%a2%e6%b8%af%e7%89%b9%e6%ae%8a%e5%be%85%e9%81%87|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===兩家VPN公司撤離香港===
虛擬私人網絡（VPN）允許用戶安全連接到世界任何一個網絡，用以保護用戶的瀏覽歷史記錄和密碼，並使用戶免受其他可疑的公共WIFI活動的侵害<ref>{{Cite web|title=What Is a VPN, and Why Would I Need One?|url=https://www.howtogeek.com/133680/htg-explains-what-is-a-vpn/|accessdate=2020-07-25|last=Hoffman|first=Chris|work=How-To Geek|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828162214/https://www.howtogeek.com/133680/htg-explains-what-is-a-vpn/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兩家VPN公司Tunnel Bear和Private Internet Access（PIA）分別在13日和14日宣布，鑑於港版國安法不明朗前景，他們會將香港服務器遷走，以保護其用戶在國安法下的隱私<ref>{{Cite web|title=Private Internet Access shuts down VPN servers in Hong Kong due to new national security law|url=https://www.privateinternetaccess.com/blog/private-internet-access-shuts-down-vpn-servers-in-hong-kong-due-to-new-national-security-law/|accessdate=2020-07-25|date=2020-07-14|work=Private Internet Access Blog|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200715063854/https://www.privateinternetaccess.com/blog/private-internet-access-shuts-down-vpn-servers-in-hong-kong-due-to-new-national-security-law/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=TunnelBear Removes Hong Kong Servers|url=https://www.tunnelbear.com/blog/tunnelbear-removes-hong-kong-servers-to-safeguard-vpn-network-infrastructure/|accessdate=2020-07-25|date=2020-07-13|work=The TunnelBear Blog|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725164432/https://www.tunnelbear.com/blog/tunnelbear-removes-hong-kong-servers-to-safeguard-vpn-network-infrastructure/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兩家公司均強調，它們不會儲存個人信息，更會繼續為香港用戶提供服務。其他VPN提供商例如SurfSharks表示正在密切關注局勢，如果收到 政府 “當局要求開始記錄用戶活動的要求”，他們將立即關閉位於香港的VPN服務器<ref>{{Cite web|title=Two top VPNs just pulled out of Hong Kong — here's why|url=https://www.tomsguide.com/news/vpns-leave-hong-kong|accessdate=2020-07-25|last=July 2020|first=Paul Wagenseil 15|work=Tom's Guide|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715214551/https://www.tomsguide.com/news/vpns-leave-hong-kong|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

